00:21:43,068 --> 00:21:45,934
You don't have to be serious,
everything doesn't have to be so serious,

249
00:21:46,003 --> 00:21:47,602
we can have fun!

250
00:21:48,468 --> 00:21:50,473
[no audible dialogue]

