00:29:06,872 --> 00:29:08,207
[dice rattling]

336
00:29:13,748 --> 00:29:14,917
[in Chinese] Three fives.

337
00:29:15,882 --> 00:29:17,853
No... five... five of...

338
00:29:17,922 --> 00:29:19,922
Ah! You cannot!
