339
00:29:20,786 --> 00:29:22,485
Ah, um...

340
00:29:23,625 --> 00:29:24,619
Five threes.

341
00:29:25,021 --> 00:29:26,126
Five...

342
00:29:27,124 --> 00:29:28,799
Six... Six threes.

