00:38:06,984 --> 00:38:08,846
[indistinct chatter]

447
00:38:12,081 --> 00:38:13,323
[in English]
What do you call this?

448
00:38:15,093 --> 00:38:17,426
- Yia me gur.
- Yia me gur.

