00:39:17,314 --> 00:39:19,818
[woman in Chinese] Eight or
four, buy eight or four!

461
00:39:21,025 --> 00:39:22,656
[indistinct chatter]

462
00:39:36,170 --> 00:39:37,539
[sizzling]

463
00:39:41,846 --> 00:39:44,337
- [in Chinese] Do you Americans have or not?
- Mm...

