00:39:45,881 --> 00:39:47,744
- [in Chinese] Smells good!
- [in Chinese] Smells good?

465
00:39:47,813 --> 00:39:49,750
- Smells good. Ah.
- Smells good.

466
00:39:49,819 --> 00:39:51,949
- [in English] Tell him.
- [in Chinese] Smells good!

467
00:39:56,691 --> 00:39:58,287
[in English]
No, not interested.

468
00:39:58,355 --> 00:39:59,823
- [in English] You have to say it louder.
- Louder?

469
00:39:59,892 --> 00:40:01,589
[in Chinese]
Smells good, master!

470
00:40:01,657 --> 00:40:03,695
- Always smells good!
- [in Chinese] Smells good, master!

